original: Lindstam, Nils Tryggve Efraim, komminister. Mönsterås, f. 11/5/06 i Annerstad, Kronob. 1., av kyrkoh. Efraim L. o. Emma Nilsson. G. 36 m. Anna-Lisa Nilsson. Barn: Margareta f. 37, Ingrid 39, Birgitta 42. — Stud:-ex. 28, teol. fil. ex. 29 samt teol. kand. o. prakt. teol. prov 34 i Lund, prästex. i Växjö, prästv. f. Växjö stift 35. Tjg. s. e. o. prästman i Mortorp, Oskar o. Hagshult, kommin. i Hagshult 38, i Mönsterås sed. 44.
translated: Lindstam, Nils Tryggve Efraim, curate. Mönsterås, born on May 11, 1906 in Annerstad, Kronoburg County. First child of the churchman Efraim L. and Emma Nilsson. Married in 1936 to Anna-Lisa Nilsson. Children: Margareta born in 1937, Ingrid in 1939, Birgitta in 1942. Completed studies at the age of 28, obtained a Bachelor's degree in theology in 1929, and a theological candidate and practical theological examination in 1934 in Lund, ordained as a priest in Växjö, received the ministerial license in the Växjö diocese in 1935. Served as an assistant curate in Mortorp, Oskar, and Hagshult, and as a curate in Hagshult from 1938. Has been serving as a curate in Mönsterås since 1944.
